Package: hpcc-connect
Version: 1.0.0
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Depends: libgtk-3-0, libblkid1, liblzma5
Maintainer: Aadhityan A <aadhityan@example.com>
Description: HPCC Connect - Cross-platform SSH Terminal Client
 A modern SSH terminal client with built-in file browser and
 drag-and-drop file transfer capabilities. Connect to HPCC
 clusters and remote servers with ease.
 .
 Features:
  - SSH terminal with full PTY support
  - Dual-pane file browser (local and remote)
  - Drag-and-drop file transfers
  - Connection management with saved credentials
  - Support for password and key-based authentication
Homepage: https://github.com/Aadhityan-A/hpcc-connect
